    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/7d3c9569b8edfe9a06a02d039df9cb39.poster.avif?t=1755179361\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/7d3c9569b8edfe9a06a02d039df9cb39.webm?t=1755179361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/7d3c9569b8edfe9a06a02d039df9cb39.mp4?t=1755179361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONE PUCK. ONE NET. ONE GOAL.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LAW 56 takes players to the future of professional hockey, where player safety is no longer a concern! Rules have changed to create the fastest and most hard hitting experience possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/7876a26ac8cd37bc0f03096a7ab44f82.poster.avif?t=1755179361\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/7876a26ac8cd37bc0f03096a7ab44f82.webm?t=1755179361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/7876a26ac8cd37bc0f03096a7ab44f82.mp4?t=1755179361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SKATE! SCRAP! SCORE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use boost pads, grind rails, and wall running to traverse arenas and incapacitate your opponents with a variety of items! Collect the puck, and fire it past the robo-goalie to run up the score, battering into your opponents along the way to gain an advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/c55e69766ea0adda6341d6884b6f8cf0.poster.avif?t=1755179361\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/c55e69766ea0adda6341d6884b6f8cf0.webm?t=1755179361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/c55e69766ea0adda6341d6884b6f8cf0.mp4?t=1755179361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FREE FOR ALL, 2V2, KRILL CONFIRMED - HUGE VARIETY!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 8 different teams to brawl it out in 8 different arenas across 3 exciting game modes to see if you have what it takes! Compete with 2-4 players to be crowned the LAW 56 CHAMPION!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras/bb11a783c52e1274aa8f0356a50df60d.avif?t=1755179361\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337370/extras_big/bb11a783c52e1274aa8f0356a50df60d.avif?t=1755179361 width=800 height=422 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
